rComments: one of the best, very helpful and you could reach her for help

I am certain Dr. Bray is a commendable physician, but ENV341 was a disgraceful waste of money, time, and resources.  She should stick to private practice, instead of trying to teach (unsuccessfully) a year's worth of material in a 1-term course.  I'd be better off reading medical journals myself, than going to her lectures.
